
<p>For my subscribers, here&rsquo;s a <a href="https://fishshell.com" title="fish shell">Fish</a> function for sending files from the current iTerm pane to another pane in the same tab.</p>

<p>When working in Forklift or Path Finder, I love the ability to send files from one pane to the other with a keyboard shortcut when browsing in split pane mode. I wanted to replicate that in iTerm. This is written for Fish, but the AppleScript it uses can easily be repurposed for other shells.</p>

